column3: here we are again... it's the 3rd time now.
you really came back for more?
I thought that maybe you could change but it seems...
like you'd only want to fight now.
I really miss the peaceful time we had at the beggining.
did you choose your final decision?
That you chose it a long time ago.
Heh. You better be ready because this time.
Heh. You thought you had a turn?
I learned from my oldest mistake buddy.
You better hope that you're going to be able to hold on.
